#: 10P1009
msgctxt "10P1009"
msgid "What's with the dead flower in the corner?"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1010
msgctxt "10P1010"
msgid "That sheriff of yours is sleeping on the job!"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1011
msgctxt "10P1011"
msgid "I have to be going now."
msgstr ""

#: 10P1101
msgctxt "10P1101"
msgid "No, I mean... it's up to me to save all humanity from being ground up into burger meat by hideous green space aliens!"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1201
msgctxt "10P1201"
msgid "I'm talking about the blue wax that got banned."
msgstr ""

#: 10P1202
msgctxt "10P1202"
msgid "Harry says that you have cases of this stuff!"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1203
msgctxt "10P1203"
msgid "Are you sure you don't have any wax?"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1204
msgctxt "10P1204"
msgid "No offense, but I'm really desperate for that wax!"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1205
msgctxt "10P1205"
msgid "Ah, forget that I asked."
msgstr ""

#: 10P1301
msgctxt "10P1301"
msgid "I didn't know that you were an animal trainer."
msgstr ""

#: 10P1302
msgctxt "10P1302"
msgid "When did you start training animals?"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1303
msgctxt "10P1303"
msgid "So you gave the sheriff a new bloodhound?"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1304
msgctxt "10P1304"
msgid "Why don't I see you at the pet shop more often?"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1305
msgctxt "10P1305"
msgid "I have to be going now."
msgstr ""

#: 10P1401
msgctxt "10P1401"
msgid "A scent-tracking pig? That's amazing!"
