#: 10P1406
msgctxt "10P1406"
msgid "Why did Perkins want that pig so badly?"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1407
msgctxt "10P1407"
msgid "Did the pig find any gold for Elmo?"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1408
msgctxt "10P1408"
msgid "Hmm, interesting story, but I have to go now."
msgstr ""

#: 10P1501
msgctxt "10P1501"
msgid "Poor guy!"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1601
msgctxt "10P1601"
msgid "You're kidding!"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1701
msgctxt "10P1701"
msgid "Yeah, uh, she's getting pretty frail these days, so she needs me to help her out around the house."
msgstr ""

#: 10P1801
msgctxt "10P1801"
msgid "What would I do with real estate?"
msgstr ""

#: 10P1802
msgctxt "10P1802"
msgid "I don't have a lot of money."
msgstr ""

#: 10P1803
msgctxt "10P1803"
msgid "Where can I get some real estate?"
