msgctxt "20N0602"
msgid "No matter. As long as I own this here island, no one's coming ashore."
msgstr ""

#: 20N0701
msgctxt "20N0701"
msgid "I ain't got no neighbors. I'm a hermit. That's what hermit means. No neighbors."
msgstr ""

#: 20N0702
msgctxt "20N0702"
msgid "What? You mean you paid cash money for that rock over there?"
msgstr ""

#: 20N0703
msgctxt "20N0703"
msgid "Oh, boy! Someone done suckered you real good!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N0704
msgctxt "20N0704"
msgid "See you later, neighbor!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N0801
msgctxt "20N0801"
msgid "Listen! I don't much care for neighbors. So if you gonna be living next door to me, you best be keeping to yourself."
msgstr ""

#: 20N0901
msgctxt "20N0901"
msgid "Is that so? I thought I smelled a fed."
msgstr ""

#: 20N0902
msgctxt "20N0902"
msgid "Agri-culture!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N0903
msgctxt "20N0903"
msgid "Why, sure I like him. I like him filled with buckshot!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N0904
msgctxt "20N0904"
msgid "Alright then, so what the heck do you want?"
msgstr ""

#: 20N1001
msgctxt "20N1001"
msgid "Required shots? I'll give you some required shots, hippie boy!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N1101
msgctxt "20N1101"
msgid "Only ones ever to come out here are fed. I can smell them a mile away."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1102
msgctxt "20N1102"
msgid "What in tarnation? Don't you be messin' with my mind, boy! Last person messin' with my mind ain't around to mess with it no more!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N1103
msgctxt "20N1103"
msgid "Are you kidding? Why, back there in the gold rush, I had me the biggest one-man mining operation going in all of Boonesville. I excavated over a hundred tons of rock. Durn near turned this island into Swiss cheese. I never found a single blasted nugget."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1104
msgctxt "20N1104"
msgid "I ain't fattenin' her up! And don't you be callin' her no pig! Her name is Truffles. I mean, she's my pet."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1201
msgctxt "20N1201"
msgid "What would you know about rough, hippie boy? Probably never worked a day in your life."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1202
msgctxt "20N1202"
msgid "Oh, some twenty years, I reckon. Of course, I'm a little too old to be mining these days."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1203
msgctxt "20N1203"
msgid "This island is pretty small, so I dumped most of the excavated rock offshore to keep them out of my way."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1204
msgctxt "20N1204"
msgid "Well, it was the gold rush, and I have to admit I had the fever real bad. In them days, you just staked your claim and started digging. Some got rich, and others busted their humps for nothing."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1205
msgctxt "20N1205"
msgid "I chose it because I value my privacy. Since it's the northernmost island, it's the farthest one from the hustle and bustle of Boonesville."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1206
msgctxt "20N1206"
msgid "Are you mocking me? I'll blast your lily white behind from here to next Tuesday!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N1207
msgctxt "20N1207"
msgid "I don't wanna see you later."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1301
msgctxt "20N1301"
msgid "Pet and food store? Hee hee! Sissy work!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N1401
msgctxt "20N1401"
msgid "Somewhere is over there to the north. Actually, right where all them bull rushes is going."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1601
msgctxt "20N1601"
msgid "I'll admit, truffles is a little overweight, but I got on a strict diet now to help me slim down."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1603
msgctxt "20N1603"
msgid "You tellin' me, she hates this whistle, squeals like a banshee every time I blow it. Now stop blowin' it when she learns to keep her greedy little snout out of my veggies."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1604
msgctxt "20N1604"
msgid "What? Don't you know what a truffle is?"
msgstr ""

#: 20N1605
msgctxt "20N1605"
msgid "I'll say, I didn't name her Truffles for nothing."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1606
msgctxt "20N1606"
msgid "Good! Now, kiss!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N1701
msgctxt "20N1701"
msgid "Oh, not again! Alright, truffles, you asked for it!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N1801
msgctxt "20N1801"
msgid "Well then, it should be obvious why I gave her that name, ya dang fool!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N1802
msgctxt "20N1802"
msgid "Jumpin' ya, hosafats! Do I have to spell it out? Truffles is a delicacy, and city folks pay big bucks for them. The reason they cost so much is cause they grow underground, and they're real hard to find. Only the snout of a highly trained pig is sensitive enough to sniff them out."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1901
msgctxt "20N1901"
msgid "Jumpin' ya, hosafats! Do I have to spell it out? Truffles is a delicacy, and city folks pay big bucks for them. The reason they cost so much is cause they grow underground, and they're real hard to find. Only the snout of a highly trained pig is sensitive enough to sniff them out."
msgstr ""

#: 20N1902
msgctxt "20N1902"
msgid "I think I'll answer just about enough of your questions, hippie boy. Now, get..."
msgstr ""

#: 20N2001
msgctxt "20N2001"
msgid "You betcha! Truth be known, truffles can sniff out most any kind of food. Why, if I gave her a carton of milk, she could find the cow it came from."
msgstr ""

#: 20N2002
msgctxt "20N2002"
msgid "What? You think I want to deal with them kooky city folk? No way! The reason I got me this pig is because I figured that if she could sniff out truffles, then surely she could sniff out some gold in my mine!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N2003
msgctxt "20N2003"
msgid "Uh, not exactly. Turns out the only thing she can smell is food. Stupid critter. I've answered enough of your questions, hippie boy! Now stop pestering me!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N2004
msgctxt "20N2004"
msgid "Good! I'm tired of talking to you anyhow!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N2101
msgctxt "20N2101"
msgid "You've been chewing loco, weed boy! I own the northernmost island, and you can't buy it, cause I ain't selling it!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N2103
msgctxt "20N2103"
msgid "Well, I'll be home-tired."
msgstr ""

#: 20N2104
msgctxt "20N2104"
msgid "Oh, no offense intended, Truffles."
msgstr ""

#: 20N2105
msgctxt "20N2105"
msgid "But... that's nothing but a pile of rock!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N2106
msgctxt "20N2106"
msgid "You better read it to me. I left my reading glasses at the library."
msgstr ""

#: 20N2107
msgctxt "20N2107"
msgid "Well, we'll just see about that."
msgstr ""

#: 20N2108
msgctxt "20N2108"
msgid "Shuffles, get over here!"
msgstr ""

#: 20N2109
msgctxt "20N2109"
msgid "Keep an eye on this young hippie boy. If he tries to come ashore, you sick him."
msgstr ""

#: 20N2110
msgctxt "20N2110"
msgid "Now, I'm gonna pay me a little visit to the town hall, and get this all straightened out."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0501
msgctxt "20P0501"
msgid "Cool it, Gramps! We're neighbors now!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P0502
msgctxt "20P0502"
msgid "Don't mind me, I'm just out for a paddle."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0503
msgctxt "20P0503"
msgid "Don't you ever get lonely out here?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P0504
msgctxt "20P0504"
msgid "Can I ask you a few questions?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P0505
msgctxt "20P0505"
msgid "I'd like to ask you a few more questions."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0506
msgctxt "20P0506"
msgid "I'd like to ask you a few more questions."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0507
msgctxt "20P0507"
msgid "I have the pig chow you ordered!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P0508
msgctxt "20P0508"
msgid "You sure you didn't order any pig chow?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P0509
msgctxt "20P0509"
msgid "Mind if I come ashore and look around?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P0510
msgctxt "20P0510"
msgid "I'd really like to come ashore."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0511
msgctxt "20P0511"
msgid "Sorry to disturb you. I'll go now."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0512
msgctxt "20P0512"
msgid "My mistake! I'm outta here!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P0601
msgctxt "20P0601"
msgid "Um, well, actually, the sign says, no trex parsenon."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0702
msgctxt "20P0702"
msgid "Well then, you're not a hermit anymore, because I just bought the island to the south of yours."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0704
msgctxt "20P0704"
msgid "Ugh, nice talking to you."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0901
msgctxt "20P0901"
msgid "Yes, sir. I'm here regarding your back taxes."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0902
msgctxt "20P0902"
msgid "Yup, I'm with the Department of Agriculture."
msgstr ""

#: 20P0903
msgctxt "20P0903"
msgid "Maybe. Do you like the fetch?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P0904
msgctxt "20P0904"
msgid "I'm no slimy money-grubbin' bureaucrat!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1001
msgctxt "20P1001"
msgid "That's right. I'm here to check that your pig has had the required shots."
msgstr ""

#: 20P1101
msgctxt "20P1101"
msgid "Why did you think I was a fed?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1102
msgctxt "20P1102"
msgid "Have you seen any space aliens out here?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1103
msgctxt "20P1103"
msgid "Do you know anything about the Big Gold Rush?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1104
msgctxt "20P1104"
msgid "Are you fattening up the pig for the fair?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1201
msgctxt "20P1201"
msgid "Not even a single nugget? That's rough."
msgstr ""

#: 20P1202
msgctxt "20P1202"
msgid "How long have you been mining?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1203
msgctxt "20P1203"
msgid "Where did you put all the excavated rock?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1204
msgctxt "20P1204"
msgid "Why did you think that there was gold here?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1205
msgctxt "20P1205"
msgid "But why this island? It's kinda out of the way."
msgstr ""

#: 20P1206
msgctxt "20P1206"
msgid "Sorry to hear about your... hump."
msgstr ""

#: 20P1207
msgctxt "20P1207"
msgid "See you later, Mr. Perkins!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1301
msgctxt "20P1301"
msgid "Well, I've never single-handedly excavated tons of rock, but I do work quite hard down at the pet and feed store."
msgstr ""

#: 20P1501
msgctxt "20P1501"
msgid "Nice talking to you, too! Sheesh!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1601
msgctxt "20P1601"
msgid "She looks like a prize porker to me."
msgstr ""

#: 20P1602
msgctxt "20P1602"
msgid "Some diet? She's eaten your whole garden!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1603
msgctxt "20P1603"
msgid "Can she ever squeal?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1604
msgctxt "20P1604"
msgid "Why did you name her Truffles?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1605
msgctxt "20P1605"
msgid "Did your pet pig do any tricks?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1606
msgctxt "20P1606"
msgid "I'll leave you and your pet pig alone now."
msgstr ""

#: 20P1801
msgctxt "20P1801"
msgid "Of course I know what truffles are!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1802
msgctxt "20P1802"
msgid "Uh, no. What are truffles?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P1901
msgctxt "20P1901"
msgid "Actually, it's still not obvious to me."
msgstr ""

#: 20P1902
msgctxt "20P1902"
msgid "Thanks for clearing that up!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P2001
msgctxt "20P2001"
msgid "Can truffles find truffles?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P2002
msgctxt "20P2002"
msgid "Are you a truffle farmer?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P2003
msgctxt "20P2003"
msgid "Did she find any gold?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P2004
msgctxt "20P2004"
msgid "Ah, that's really interesting, but I have to go."
msgstr ""

#: 20P2101
msgctxt "20P2101"
msgid "Yeah, yeah, I know it's private property, cause I just bought it!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P2102
msgctxt "20P2102"
msgid "Northernmost island? Now why would I want that wee bitty thing over there?"
msgstr ""

#: 20P2106
msgctxt "20P2106"
msgid "Yeah, but it's the northernmost pile of rock, which means you own it! You're standing on the first island to the south of the northernmost island, and I have a deed right here that says I own it!"
msgstr ""

#: 20P2107
msgctxt "20P2107"
msgid "It says that you're on my island, so kindly remove yourself from it."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0301
msgctxt "21N0301"
msgid "Oh, yeah, you see, the thing is, we were sort of like for a gig, you know."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0302
msgctxt "21N0302"
msgid "Huh, I'll say. I can't even find this dreary little bird on the map."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0303
msgctxt "21N0303"
msgid "Oh, well, our gig is in... the gig is... Where was we going again, love?"
msgstr ""

#: 21N0304
msgctxt "21N0304"
msgid "Oh, I don't know. I must have taken a wrong turn somewhere."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0305
msgctxt "21N0305"
msgid "Well, I'll be the judge of that if you don't mind. I'm the one with the map, you know."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0306
msgctxt "21N0306"
msgid "Why, heavy metal, of course! With the metal minstrels! Haven't you heard of us?"
msgstr ""

#: 21N0307
msgctxt "21N0307"
msgid "Well, we don't have any roadies. Roxy and I, we split up the driving, and Drums, he takes care of the equipment before and after each show."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0308
msgctxt "21N0308"
msgid "Well, it's because drums can't talk. He doesn't got a tongue anymore, you see."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0309
msgctxt "21N0309"
msgid "Well, because he can't, you see. He doesn't got a tongue anymore."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0310
msgctxt "21N0310"
msgid "It was a party a few years ago. Quite tragic, really. Mr. Showoff was trying to impress some birds by biting the head off a bat. Unfortunately, in the process, he also bit off most of his tongue."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0311
msgctxt "21N0311"
msgid "Just a pause..."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0401
msgctxt "21N0401"
msgid "We had plenty of time to get there before you took the wheel. I can't even catch a few Z's without you getting us into some kind of trouble."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0501
msgctxt "21N0501"
msgid "You must have taken a lot of long turns to get us here. What is this place anyways?"
msgstr ""

#: 21N0502
msgctxt "21N0502"
msgid "You're not kidding!"
msgstr ""

#: 21N0601
msgctxt "21N0601"
msgid "I was only asleep five hours. How could you get us this lost? I'm warning you right now, Vipe. I'll be so steamed if we end up missing this gig."
msgstr ""

#: 21N0701
msgctxt "21N0701"
msgid "You mean you've been driving for five hours and you don't even know where we're going? Ugh! You are just amazing, Vipe! You're a real piece of work! I should have listened to my mother and become a professional tattoo artist!"
msgstr ""

#: 21N0801
msgctxt "21N0801"
msgid "Well, perhaps you've heard of our songs, then. You know, Love Me Like a Reptile. The Bottom Me Lady! Give Annika a chance. How about Tattoo Biker Chick? I Think I Love You. Remember that?"
msgstr ""

#: 21N0901
msgctxt "21N0901"
msgid "I think that you and Drums should trade jobs. He can do the driving and you can take care of the gear. Who knows? Maybe then we'd get to where we're supposed to be once in a while."
msgstr ""

#: 21N1001
msgctxt "21N1001"
msgid "Oh, for Pete's sake! It's in Toledo!"
msgstr ""

#: 21N1002
msgctxt "21N1002"
msgid "Oh, sure we are. We have to be."
msgstr ""

#: 21N1003
msgctxt "21N1003"
msgid "Right, bye!"
msgstr ""

#: 21N1101
msgctxt "21N1101"
msgid "Oh yeah, Toledo. Oh, now I remember."
msgstr ""

#: 21N1102
msgctxt "21N1102"
msgid "Vipe, your pants must be too tight, cause it's obvious you are not getting enough blood flow to your brain."
msgstr ""

#: 21N1201
msgctxt "21N1201"
msgid "Look, there's no way he could have taken us that far off course. Now get lost! I gotta figure out how to get us into Toledo by 7."
msgstr ""

#: 21N1301
msgctxt "21N1301"
msgid "Well, it wasn't a real bat. You know, it was made out of chocolate. Although, I have to admit, when the blood started gushing out of his mouth, the whole thing started to look awfully authentic."
msgstr ""

#: 21N1302
msgctxt "21N1302"
msgid "Well, our drums has a terrible sweet tooth, especially when it comes to chocolate. He's a certified chocoholic."
msgstr ""

#: 21N1303
msgctxt "21N1303"
msgid "Yeah, you might say he bit off a little more than he could chew, eh?"
msgstr ""

#: 21N1304
msgctxt "21N1304"
msgid "Just a pause..."
msgstr ""

#: 21P0301
msgctxt "21P0301"
msgid "You look kinda stressed out, mister."
msgstr ""

#: 21P0302
msgctxt "21P0302"
msgid "Are you guys lost?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0303
msgctxt "21P0303"
msgid "Where's your gig?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0304
msgctxt "21P0304"
msgid "Well, how did you end up all the way out here?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0305
msgctxt "21P0305"
msgid "I'm telling ya, you're nowhere near Toledo!"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0306
msgctxt "21P0306"
msgid "What kind of music do you guys play?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0307
msgctxt "21P0307"
msgid "Where are all your roadies?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0308
msgctxt "21P0308"
msgid "Hmm, your drummer sure isn't a talkative sort, is he?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0309
msgctxt "21P0309"
msgid "Why won't your drummer talk to me?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0310
msgctxt "21P0310"
msgid "How did your drummer lose his tongue?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0311
msgctxt "21P0311"
msgid "Gotta go!"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0502
msgctxt "21P0502"
msgid "It's Boonesville!"
msgstr ""

#: 21P0802
msgctxt "21P0802"
msgid "They don't ring a bell either."
msgstr ""

#: 21P1001
msgctxt "21P1001"
msgid "Do any of you know where your gig is?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P1002
msgctxt "21P1002"
msgid "I'm sorry to tell you, but you're nowhere near Toledo."
msgstr ""

#: 21P1003
msgctxt "21P1003"
msgid "Gotta go!"
msgstr ""

#: 21P1201
msgctxt "21P1201"
msgid "I ought to know. I live here."
msgstr ""

#: 21P1301
msgctxt "21P1301"
msgid "A bat? That's cruel! Not to mention disgusting!"
msgstr ""

#: 21P1302
msgctxt "21P1302"
msgid "Why a chocolate bat?"
msgstr ""

#: 21P1303
msgctxt "21P1303"
msgid "He bit off his own tongue? Ouch!"
msgstr ""

#: 21P1304
msgctxt "21P1304"
msgid "Gotta go!"
msgstr ""

#: 22N0201
msgctxt "22N0201"
msgid "Look, kid, I don't have time for autographs right now, so go away!"
msgstr ""

#: 22N03011
msgctxt "22N03011"
msgid "I said, get lost!"
msgstr ""

#: 22N03012
msgctxt "22N03012"
msgid "I'm kinda busy here, so go away!"
msgstr ""

#: 22N03013
msgctxt "22N03013"
msgid "Look, I have a black belt, so you better stop bugging me."
msgstr ""

#: 22P0201
msgctxt "22P0201"
msgid "Uh, excuse me."
msgstr ""

#: 23P0301
msgctxt "23P0301"
msgid "Can you talk?"
msgstr ""

#: 23P0302
msgctxt "23P0302"
msgid "Do they argue like that all the time?"
msgstr ""

#: 23P0303
msgctxt "23P0303"
msgid "They must drive you crazy!"
msgstr ""

#: 23P0304
msgctxt "23P0304"
msgid "I'm sorry to hear about your tongue. Did it hurt?"
msgstr ""

#: 23P0305
msgctxt "23P0305"
msgid "I hear that you are a real chocolate fiend!"
msgstr ""

#: 23P0306
msgctxt "23P0306"
msgid "Would you believe that I've been abducted by aliens?"
msgstr ""

#: 23P0307
msgctxt "23P0307"
msgid "Could you stop drumming for just a minute?"
msgstr ""

#: 23P0308
msgctxt "23P0308"
msgid "I gotta go now."
msgstr ""

#: 23P0601
msgctxt "23P0601"
msgid "Well, at least I know why you're so quiet now. I guess you could say that the bat's got your tongue."
msgstr ""

#: 300W001
msgctxt "300W001"
msgid "I can't take that!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W002
msgctxt "300W002"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

#: 300W003
msgctxt "300W003"
msgid "I can't take that."
msgstr ""

#: 300W004
msgctxt "300W004"
msgid "Nah."
msgstr ""

#: 300W005
msgctxt "300W005"
msgid "I can't use that!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W006
msgctxt "300W006"
msgid "Yuck! Just looking at this thing could turn me into a vegetarian!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W007
msgctxt "300W007"
msgid "Here, Piggy, Piggy, Piggy, come and get it! Have a yummy Orion burger!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W008
msgctxt "300W008"
msgid "Wow! Look at her wolf it down. She must not have any taste buds."
msgstr ""

#: 300W009
msgctxt "300W009"
msgid "That's it. Go find the rest of that burger. Work that sniffer, girl!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W010
msgctxt "300W010"
msgid "Here, Piggy Piggy!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W011
msgctxt "300W011"
msgid "I'm not cooking that."
msgstr ""

#: 300W012
msgctxt "300W012"
msgid "She sure has her heart set on that burger!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W013
msgctxt "300W013"
msgid "I'm not putting my lips on that thing again. My stomach's been through enough."
msgstr ""

#: 300W014
msgctxt "300W014"
msgid "I can't do that with a burger morsel."
msgstr ""

#: 300W015
msgctxt "300W015"
msgid "The cover reads, Complements of Cartwright Excavation Equipment."
msgstr ""

#: 300W016
msgctxt "300W016"
msgid "This is no time for a barbecue. Besides, I don't like pork chops."
msgstr ""

#: 300W017
msgctxt "300W017"
msgid "Aunt Polly told me never to play with matches."
msgstr ""

#: 300W018
msgctxt "300W018"
msgid "I'll need more than matches to get that thing to fly again."
msgstr ""

#: 300W019
msgctxt "300W019"
msgid "Can't light soggy wood."
msgstr ""

#: 300W020
msgctxt "300W020"
msgid "I don't have time to cook just now."
msgstr ""

#: 300W021
msgctxt "300W021"
msgid "I don't need matches for that. It has a pull cord."
msgstr ""

#: 300W022
msgctxt "300W022"
msgid "That's not gonna work. It's toast!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W023
msgctxt "300W023"
msgid "Well, that ain't gonna work."
msgstr ""

#: 300W024
msgctxt "300W024"
msgid "I don't have anything to burn."
msgstr ""

#: 300W025
msgctxt "300W025"
msgid "I can't like that."
msgstr ""

#: 300W026
msgctxt "300W026"
msgid "Hmm, it's kind of hard to read his writing on this empty jug, but I think the label says, Perkins Private Reserve Hooch, aged two weeks. Ha! He even spelled XXX wrong."
msgstr ""

#: 300W027
msgctxt "300W027"
msgid "The jug's empty."
msgstr ""

#: 300W028
msgctxt "300W028"
msgid "It's empty."
msgstr ""

#: 300W029
msgctxt "300W029"
msgid "I can't use the jug on that."
msgstr ""

#: 300W030
msgctxt "300W030"
msgid "Distilled carrot juice. Yum!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W031
msgctxt "300W031"
msgid "I better not waste that on truffles. I might need it later on."
msgstr ""

#: 300W032
msgctxt "300W032"
msgid "I don't think that carrot juice is going to get this heap going."
msgstr ""

#: 300W033
msgctxt "300W033"
msgid "The burner uses propane, not distilled carrot juice."
msgstr ""

#: 300W034
msgctxt "300W034"
msgid "It's already distilled!"
msgstr ""

#: 300W035
msgctxt "300W035"
msgid "Boiling the carrot juice won't help."
msgstr ""

#: 300W035Z
msgctxt "300W035Z"
msgid "That probably wouldn't be too smart."
msgstr ""

