#: 35N1502
msgctxt "35N1502"
msgid "Well, I'm going for a real Art Nouveau motif. Imagine, if you will, a chrome Venus de Milo in the corner next to the fake flamingo pond. The seats are covered with a nice leopard skin vinyl. There's bangles and dingle balls around every window. Oh, and there's neon lights everywhere!"
