msgid "You should know better than to pester a hungry bork."
msgstr ""

#: 512F001B
msgctxt "512F001B"
msgid "Hahaha! How humiliating for you, human!"
msgstr ""

#: 512F001C
msgctxt "512F001C"
msgid "Nice going, you useless waste of protoplasm!"
msgstr ""

#: 512F002A
msgctxt "512F002A"
msgid "What? Were you trying to cook yourself before we turn you into a burger? Crazy!"
msgstr ""

#: 512F003A
msgctxt "512F003A"
msgid "The Borks have a word for creatures like you, gogobungo. Roughly translated, it means loser!"
msgstr ""

#: 512F003B
msgctxt "512F003B"
msgid "Oh, I can hardly wait to smother you with our secret sauce!"
msgstr ""

#: 513W001
msgctxt "513W001"
msgid "Hey, where's my aunt? Is she in there?"
msgstr ""

#: 513W002
msgctxt "513W002"
msgid "Where is she?"
msgstr ""

#: 513W003
msgctxt "513W003"
msgid "Oh, you didn't!"
msgstr ""

#: 513W005
msgctxt "513W005"
msgid "Oh, you animal!"
msgstr ""

#: 513W006
msgctxt "513W006"
msgid "What? Eating my ant is supposed to make me happy?"
msgstr ""

#: 513Z002
msgctxt "513Z002"
msgid "Easy now. You'll never pass the last test anyway, so what's the difference?"
msgstr ""

#: 513Z003
msgctxt "513Z003"
msgid "Take heart in the fact that this was a much less painful fate than when I harvest the rest of your planet."
msgstr ""

#: 513Z004
msgctxt "513Z004"
msgid "Phew! There is just no place in this human."
msgstr ""

#: 513Z005
msgctxt "513Z005"
msgid "Put a break with him!"
msgstr ""

#: 513Z006
msgctxt "513Z006"
msgid "If this human thinks he knows how to make people happy, then that will be his final test!"
msgstr ""

#: 51N0101
msgctxt "51N0101"
msgid "Shh! Keep it down! I'm on your side!"
msgstr ""

#: 51N0102
msgctxt "51N0102"
msgid "The side that's trying to prevent creatures like you from being ground up into burger meat."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0201
msgctxt "51N0201"
msgid "My name is Astral. I'm a member of the Planet Huggers."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0202
msgctxt "51N0202"
msgid "I mean total bio-extermination. Well, if you fail one of their intelligence tests, you'll see for yourself how awful it is."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0203
msgctxt "51N0203"
msgid "Well, aside from getting my jumpsuit completely filthy, I'm spying on Zlark. I'm trying to collect evidence that intelligent lifeforms are being illegally harvested."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0204
msgctxt "51N0204"
msgid "They have to test you because they aren't supposed to harvest intelligent life forms. Intelligent life is a very scarce resource in the universe."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0205
msgctxt "51N0205"
msgid "I wouldn't count on it. You don't look all that bright to me."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0206
msgctxt "51N0206"
msgid "I was just scanning your DNA for our records. I didn't mean for you to catch me. You weren't moving, so I figured that you had passed out, or that you were dead."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0301
msgctxt "51N0301"
msgid "It's an organization dedicated to the preservation of intelligent life throughout the galaxy. We oppose Orion Burger's barbaric process of planetary destruction. But we meet on the first Thursday of every month."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0401
msgctxt "51N0401"
msgid "I'm sorry to say that I've seen the protein harvesters perform their ghastly work. Orion Burger wiped out my home planet several years ago, and as far as I know, I'm the only survivor."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0501
msgctxt "51N0501"
msgid "You got that right. I'm a stowaway. Oh, if Zlark found out I was here, I'd be history. Whatever you do, don't let him know that I'm here."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0701
msgctxt "51N0701"
msgid "The tests aren't supposed to hurt."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0801
msgctxt "51N0801"
msgid "Come on, look around out there. Not many survive their neuroanalysis test."
msgstr ""

#: 51N0901
msgctxt "51N0901"
msgid "Quickly, get away from the vent. And remember, you never saw me."
msgstr ""

#: 51P0102
msgctxt "51P0102"
msgid "Uh, exactly what side would that be?"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0103
msgctxt "51P0103"
msgid "Oh, well, that definitely sounds like the side that I'm on."
msgstr ""

#: 51P0201
msgctxt "51P0201"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0202
msgctxt "51P0202"
msgid "What do you mean exactly by planetary destruction?"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0203
msgctxt "51P0203"
msgid "What are you doing in the ventilation duct?"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0204
msgctxt "51P0204"
msgid "Why the IQ tests? Why don't they just eat me?"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0205
msgctxt "51P0205"
msgid "What are my chances for passing these tests?"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0206
msgctxt "51P0206"
msgid "What was that thing you were waving in my face?"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0301
msgctxt "51P0301"
msgid "What are planet huggers?"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0402
msgctxt "51P0402"
msgid "That's terrible! And now they're planning to do the same thing to my planet!"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0403
msgctxt "51P0403"
msgid "Just when I thought my life couldn't get any worse, now I'm not even at the top of the food chain anymore."
msgstr ""

#: 51P0501
msgctxt "51P0501"
msgid "So, you're sneaking around through this ship, and those green guys don't even know that you're in here?"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0601
msgctxt "51P0601"
msgid "Yeah, I've noticed."
msgstr ""

#: 51P0701
msgctxt "51P0701"
msgid "Hey, I'll have you know that if they can stand the screaming, I can stand the pain."
msgstr ""

#: 51P0702
msgctxt "51P0702"
msgid "Those bozos were just zapping my head with electricity! It didn't exactly tickle."
msgstr ""

#: 51P0801
msgctxt "51P0801"
msgid "Dead!"
msgstr ""

#: 51P0802
msgctxt "51P0802"
msgid "Hmm, I see what you mean."
msgstr ""

#: 51P0901
msgctxt "51P0901"
msgid "Uh-oh! I think I hear someone coming!"
msgstr ""

#: 52N0101
msgctxt "52N0101"
msgid "How do you know my name? And how did you know I was in here?"
msgstr ""

#: 52N0102
msgctxt "52N0102"
msgid "A time warp?"
msgstr ""

#: 52N0103
msgctxt "52N0103"
msgid "Oh, well, I was monkeying around with the neutrino pulse gun controls a little while ago, but I didn't think it would cause a time warp to happen. Hmm, fascinating."
msgstr ""

#: 52N0201
msgctxt "52N0201"
msgid "What for?"
msgstr ""

#: 52N0202
msgctxt "52N0202"
msgid "Cage? You humans live in cages?"
msgstr ""

#: 52N0203
msgctxt "52N0203"
msgid "The Planet Huggers will use it to generate bad publicity for Orion Burger. We might even be able to put them out of business!"
msgstr ""

#: 52N0204
msgctxt "52N0204"
msgid "Mutants? Do they have laser guns?"
msgstr ""

#: 52N0205
msgctxt "52N0205"
msgid "Knowing Zlark, the ray gun he gave you is probably barely powerful enough to defrost his lunch."
msgstr ""

#: 52N0206
msgctxt "52N0206"
msgid "They home in on life signs. Perhaps you could run around quickly and confuse their targeting systems and get them to zap each other."
msgstr ""

#: 52N0207
msgctxt "52N0207"
msgid "No problem. But just remember, don't let them find out that you're in a time warp."
msgstr ""

#: 52N0301
msgctxt "52N0301"
msgid "Oh, well, you're very welcome."
msgstr ""

#: 52N0401
msgctxt "52N0401"
msgid "Oh, well, in that case, Zlarg is already cheating. This is just the sort of evidence I was hoping to collect. His test scenarios are supposed to reflect your natural habitat."
msgstr ""

#: 52N0501
msgctxt "52N0501"
msgid "Hmm... clearly you'll have to eliminate these mutant gerbils before escape from the cage is possible."
msgstr ""

#: 52N0601
msgctxt "52N0601"
msgid "It sounds to me as if the only thing in that case that can destroy the mutant gerbils are the mutant gerbils themselves."
msgstr ""

#: 52P0101
msgctxt "52P0101"
msgid "Psst, OSTRO!"
msgstr ""

#: 52P0102
msgctxt "52P0102"
msgid "I've talked with you before. I'm in some kind of time warp. I've been reliving the day over and over again."
msgstr ""

#: 52P0103
msgctxt "52P0103"
msgid "It has something to do with that abductotron machine. I think there was some kind of malfunction."
msgstr ""

#: 52P0201
msgctxt "52P0201"
msgid "Thanks a lot!"
msgstr ""

#: 52P0202
msgctxt "52P0202"
msgid "I can't figure out how to escape from the cage!"
msgstr ""

#: 52P0203
msgctxt "52P0203"
msgid "What do you plan to do with this evidence?"
msgstr ""

#: 52P0204
msgctxt "52P0204"
msgid "Speaking of gerbils, those mutants are trying to kill me!"
msgstr ""

#: 52P0205
msgctxt "52P0205"
msgid "Zlar gave me a ray gun too."
msgstr ""

#: 52P0206
msgctxt "52P0206"
msgid "How can I get them to destroy each other?"
msgstr ""

#: 52P0207
msgctxt "52P0207"
msgid "Thanks for the advice!"
msgstr ""

#: 52P0301
msgctxt "52P0301"
msgid "You brought me some extra time to pass these crazy tests. Actually, an infinite amount of time."
msgstr ""

#: 52P0401
msgctxt "52P0401"
msgid "Of course not!"
msgstr ""

#: 52P0402
msgctxt "52P0402"
msgid "I can assure you, that cage is my gerbil's natural habitat, not mine."
msgstr ""

#: 52P0501
msgctxt "52P0501"
msgid "Yeah, big ones!"
msgstr ""

#: 52P0601
msgctxt "52P0601"
msgid "It is pretty cheesy."
msgstr ""

#: 53N0102
msgctxt "53N0102"
msgid "I wouldn't expect a lot of courtesy from them, especially not from Zlarg. Every time you pass one of his tests, you're delaying his harvest. Ha! I'll bet that you're really starting to try what little patience he has."
msgstr ""

#: 53N0103
msgctxt "53N0103"
msgid "He eats. He eats all the time. It's no wonder those gluttons need such a huge supply of protein for their restaurants."
msgstr ""

#: 53N0104
msgctxt "53N0104"
msgid "That's the spirit!"
msgstr ""

#: 53P0101
msgctxt "53P0101"
msgid "Ow! Watch it, you bubble-blowing buffoon!"
msgstr ""

#: 53P0102
msgctxt "53P0102"
msgid "Oh, I wish those aliens would treat their guests with a little more courtesy."
msgstr ""

#: 53P0103
msgctxt "53P0103"
msgid "Poor guy... uh, by the way, what does he do while I'm working on one of his tests?"
msgstr ""

#: 53P0104
msgctxt "53P0104"
msgid "Well, glutton or not, he's not getting his tentacles on any of my protein."
msgstr ""

#: 53P0105
msgctxt "53P0105"
msgid "Uh, I hear someone coming. I'll talk to you later."
msgstr ""

#: 54N0101
msgctxt "54N0101"
msgid "Is that so?"
msgstr ""

#: 54N0102
msgctxt "54N0102"
msgid "An Orion burger. Ugh. Well, that shouldn't be so hard to find. Just follow its disgusting smell."
msgstr ""

#: 54N0201
msgctxt "54N0201"
msgid "Ugh, you actually put one of those things in your mouth?"
msgstr ""

#: 54N0202
msgctxt "54N0202"
msgid "Really? I can practically smell the stench of one of those things through the void of space."
msgstr ""

#: 54N0203
msgctxt "54N0203"
msgid "Well, if your nose can't track an intensely pungent burger, chances are your other senses aren't particularly strong either. Maybe you should try to amplify them somehow."
msgstr ""

#: 54N0401
msgctxt "54N0401"
msgid "That's too bad. Sounds like you have a bit of a problem, then. We are talking about a test of your sensory perception, after all."
msgstr ""

#: 54P0101
msgctxt "54P0101"
msgid "Man, that sensory test is really hard!"
msgstr ""

#: 54P0102
msgctxt "54P0102"
msgid "Yeah, it's some kind of treasure hunt. I'm supposed to find a hidden Orion burger."
msgstr ""

#: 54P0201
msgctxt "54P0201"
msgid "It smells disgusting, but it tastes even worse!"
msgstr ""

#: 54P0202
msgctxt "54P0202"
msgid "I can't follow the burger's smell. It's too far away."
msgstr ""

#: 54P0203
msgctxt "54P0203"
msgid "Do you have any other suggestions?"
msgstr ""

#: 54P0301
msgctxt "54P0301"
msgid "Zlar didn't exactly give me a choice in the matter."
msgstr ""

#: 54P0401
msgctxt "54P0401"
msgid "I guess my nose isn't as sensitive as yours."
msgstr ""

#: 54P0501
msgctxt "54P0501"
msgid "Amplify my senses. I'll have to give that some thought."
msgstr ""

#: 55N0101
msgctxt "55N0101"
msgid "You passed another test!"
msgstr ""

#: 55N0102
msgctxt "55N0102"
msgid "Sorry. Hey, who knows? Maybe there is hope for you earthlings this time after all."
msgstr ""

#: 55N0103
msgctxt "55N0103"
msgid "Well, according to our records, Orion Burger harvested your planet once before, some 50 million years ago."
msgstr ""

#: 55N0104
msgctxt "55N0104"
msgid "The protein harvesters must have accidentally left behind enough genetic material to allow life to re-establish itself."
msgstr ""

#: 55P0102
msgctxt "55P0102"
msgid "Yeah. Well, you don't have to act so surprised about it."
msgstr ""

#: 55P0103
msgctxt "55P0103"
msgid "This time? What do you mean, this time?"
msgstr ""

#: 55P0104
msgctxt "55P0104"
msgid "50 million years ago? Oh, man! You mean to say that the dinosaurs disappeared because they were made into Orion burgers?"
msgstr ""

#: 55P0105
msgctxt "55P0105"
msgid "So that's what Zlarg meant when he said that the Earth was a second-growth planet. Beautiful! I think I need to lie down for a minute."
msgstr ""

#: 56N0101
msgctxt "56N0101"
msgid "What's the problem?"
msgstr ""

#: 56N0102
msgctxt "56N0102"
msgid "Could you be a little more specific? I mean, what do they look like?"
msgstr ""

#: 56N0103
msgctxt "56N0103"
msgid "Borks? Oh, no! Those are nasty little pets!"
msgstr ""

#: 56N0201
msgctxt "56N0201"
msgid "I'll say. I once had one eat a hole right through the hull of my spaceship while I was trying to maneuver my way through an asteroid belt. I was fortunate to get out of that unpleasant situation in one piece."
msgstr ""

#: 56N0202
msgctxt "56N0202"
msgid "Hmm, I'm not surprised. You're obviously going to have to learn a little Borkese so that you can decipher these instructions."
msgstr ""

#: 56N0203
msgctxt "56N0203"
msgid "No, I don't. But I'm sure their language is relatively simple. They are pretty mindless creatures after all."
msgstr ""

#: 56N0204
msgctxt "56N0204"
msgid "Well, when I'm visiting a foreign planet and I need to pick up the local lingo, I'll often watch what people are doing and listen to what they're saying. That way I can associate their words with their actions, which allows me to build up a rough working knowledge of the language fairly quickly."
msgstr ""

#: 56N0205
msgctxt "56N0205"
msgid "Did they give you a gizmo with rainbow colored buttons?"
msgstr ""

#: 56N0206
msgctxt "56N0206"
msgid "Give me a break. I'm having a really bad hair day. It just loses all of its body in these damp ventilation ducts."
msgstr ""

#: 56N0207
msgctxt "56N0207"
msgid "See you later!"
msgstr ""

#: 56N0401
msgctxt "56N0401"
msgid "And you just told me that the borax will rainbow color too."
msgstr ""

#: 56N0501
msgctxt "56N0501"
msgid "I hate these undercover assignments. At least I remember to bring my mirror along with me this time."
msgstr ""

#: 56P0101
msgctxt "56P0101"
msgid "Psst! Astral, I'm having a bit of trouble with this language test."
msgstr ""

#: 56P0102
msgctxt "56P0102"
msgid "Well, I have to exterminate a bunch of weird little space critters."
msgstr ""

#: 56P0103
msgctxt "56P0103"
msgid "Well, they're fat, and rainbow-colored, and all they ever seem to do is eat and destroy things. Zlarg called them __________?"
msgstr ""

#: 56P0201
msgctxt "56P0201"
msgid "You're familiar with books?"
msgstr ""

#: 56P0202
msgctxt "56P0202"
msgid "The extermination instructions I was given are in bork ease."
msgstr ""

#: 56P0203
msgctxt "56P0203"
msgid "Do you know how to speak, Borkies?"
msgstr ""

#: 56P0204
msgctxt "56P0204"
msgid "How am I ever going to learn to speak Borkese?"
msgstr ""

#: 56P0205
msgctxt "56P0205"
msgid "How will I know which instruction to use for each block?"
msgstr ""

#: 56P0206
msgctxt "56P0206"
msgid "You sure spend a lot of time fussing with your hair."
msgstr ""

#: 56P0207
msgctxt "56P0207"
msgid "I better get going. I don't want to get caught talking to you."
msgstr ""

#: 56P0301
msgctxt "56P0301"
msgid "You know? That's so crazy, it just might work!"
msgstr ""

#: 56P0401
msgctxt "56P0401"
msgid "Yeah?"
msgstr ""

#: 56P0402
msgctxt "56P0402"
msgid "Yeah? Oh, of course! The buttons are color-coded! Boy, is my face red."
msgstr ""

#: 56P0501
msgctxt "56P0501"
msgid "That's awful. I wouldn't want your hair to be all limp when my planet gets harvested."
msgstr ""

#: 57N0101
msgctxt "57N0101"
msgid "Yes, I know. I witnessed the whole thing. It was awful. I'm so sorry."
msgstr ""

#: 57N0201
msgctxt "57N0201"
msgid "Come on, Wilbur. You can't afford to get all emotional right now. You have to pull yourself together for the logic test."
msgstr ""

#: 57N0202
msgctxt "57N0202"
msgid "The bigger they are, the harder they fall."
msgstr ""

#: 57N0203
msgctxt "57N0203"
msgid "You can't give up, Wilbur. Zlard may have eaten your ant, but you can still stop him from harvesting the rest of your planet."
msgstr ""

#: 57N0204
msgctxt "57N0204"
msgid "If you pass, your planet becomes a fully sanctioned intergalactic refuge for developing intelligent lifeforms. As such, Zlarg would have no choice but to call off the harvest."
msgstr ""

#: 57N0205
msgctxt "57N0205"
msgid "Okay, Wilbur."
msgstr ""

#: 57N0401
msgctxt "57N0401"
msgid "That's the spirit. Besides, you are almost there. The logic test is the last one."
msgstr ""

#: 57N0501
msgctxt "57N0501"
msgid "True, but he knows that the planet huggers are watching. He won't take that chance."
msgstr ""

#: 57P0101
msgctxt "57P0101"
msgid "That big green animal just ate my Aunt Polly!"
msgstr ""

#: 57P0201
msgctxt "57P0201"
msgid "Why did he have to drag my Aunt Polly into this?"
msgstr ""

#: 57P0202
msgctxt "57P0202"
msgid "Oh, Zlarg is gonna pay for this!"
msgstr ""

#: 57P0203
msgctxt "57P0203"
msgid "What do I do now? These tests are hopeless!"
msgstr ""

#: 57P0204
msgctxt "57P0204"
msgid "What happens if I pass this last test?"
msgstr ""

#: 57P0205
msgctxt "57P0205"
msgid "I'll talk to you later. I have to collect my thoughts."
msgstr ""

#: 57P0301
msgctxt "57P0301"
msgid "Yeah? Well, then Zlar's gonna fall awfully hard!"
msgstr ""

#: 57P0401
msgctxt "57P0401"
msgid "Yeah, you're right. I'll pass these stupid tests... somehow."
msgstr ""

#: 57P0402
msgctxt "57P0402"
msgid "HALLELUJAH!"
msgstr ""

#: 57P0501
msgctxt "57P0501"
msgid "What? Zlarg call off the harvest? I wouldn't trust that big blowhard any further than I could throw him!"
msgstr ""

#: 57P0502
msgctxt "57P0502"
msgid "Ha! If he only knew how closely you're watching him!"
msgstr ""

#: 58N0101
msgctxt "58N0101"
msgid "What is it now?"
msgstr ""

#: 58N0102
msgctxt "58N0102"
msgid "Make people happy? Well, sounds like you have your work cut out for you. I mean, no offense, but you humans do get a little over-emotional at times and..."
msgstr ""

#: 58N0103
msgctxt "58N0103"
msgid "See what I mean? In any event, I don't think that I can help you this time. You know a lot more about humans than I do."
msgstr ""

#: 58N0104
msgctxt "58N0104"
msgid "Look, now that's not very logical either."
msgstr ""

#: 58P0101
msgctxt "58P0101"
msgid "Psst. ASTRO!"
msgstr ""

#: 58P0102
msgctxt "58P0102"
msgid "I could really use some help with this crazy logic test. I have to figure out how to make a bunch of people happy."
msgstr ""

#: 58P0103
msgctxt "58P0103"
msgid "Astro, are you gonna help me out or what?"
msgstr ""

#: 58P0104
msgctxt "58P0104"
msgid "I suppose you're right. Well, at least wish me luck."
msgstr ""

#: 58P0105
msgctxt "58P0105"
msgid "Oh, never mind. Uh-oh, I hear someone coming!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W001
msgctxt "600W001"
msgid "Wow! My very own space blaster!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W002
msgctxt "600W002"
msgid "These ray guns seem much more powerful on TV."
msgstr ""

#: 600W003
msgctxt "600W003"
msgid "I'd better not."
msgstr ""

#: 600W004
msgctxt "600W004"
msgid "Nah, why bother?"
msgstr ""

#: 600W005
msgctxt "600W005"
msgid "I couldn't do that!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W006
msgctxt "600W006"
msgid "Fat lot of good that did."
msgstr ""

#: 600W007
msgctxt "600W007"
msgid "Nah."
msgstr ""

#: 600W008
msgctxt "600W008"
msgid "Wow! Look at him go!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W008Z
msgctxt "600W008Z"
msgid "Nah, there's kibble all over the floor."
msgstr ""

#: 600W009
msgctxt "600W009"
msgid "I don't think they want to eat kibble. I think they want to eat me!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W010
msgctxt "600W010"
msgid "Nah!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W011A
msgctxt "600W011A"
msgid "WHAAAAAAAT!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W011B
msgctxt "600W011B"
msgid "WHAAAAAAAT?! OOF!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W011C
msgctxt "600W011C"
msgid "Waaaaah!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W011D
msgctxt "600W011D"
msgid "Wow, wow, wow!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W011E
msgctxt "600W011E"
msgid "Yeah! Oh, wow!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W011F
msgctxt "600W011F"
msgid "No! No!"
msgstr ""

#: 600W012
msgctxt "600W012"
msgid "It's dangerous walking around in here with Kibble on the floor."
msgstr ""

#: 600W013
msgctxt "600W013"
msgid "Oh, that'll help."
msgstr ""

#: 600W014
msgctxt "600W014"
msgid "I think they are angry enough already."
msgstr ""

#: 601F001
msgctxt "601F001"
msgid "You are a lot heavier than you look, human."
msgstr ""

#: 601F003
msgctxt "601F003"
msgid "Sorry, boss. Didn't mean to bruise our dinner."
msgstr ""

#: 601W001
msgctxt "601W001"
msgid "Whoa!"
msgstr ""

#: 601W002
msgctxt "601W002"
msgid "Um... what's my gerbil cage doing here?"
msgstr ""

#: 601Z001
msgctxt "601Z001"
msgid "The nerve of that Earthling passing one of my tests!"
msgstr ""

#: 601Z003
msgctxt "601Z003"
msgid "Well, he won't feel like such a big man after he steps under my shrink."
msgstr ""

#: 601Z004
msgctxt "601Z004"
msgid "Easy, you idiot! We might be eatin' them later!"
msgstr ""

#: 601Z005
msgctxt "601Z005"
msgid "Alright, human. You squeaked by the first test, but that was the easy part. Now we start testing your higher mental functions, beginning with your survival instincts!"
msgstr ""

#: 601Z006
msgctxt "601Z006"
msgid "You about to find out!"
msgstr ""

#: 601Z007
msgctxt "601Z007"
msgid "Flemix! Activate! The Shrink!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W001
msgctxt "602W001"
msgid "Whoa!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W002
msgctxt "602W002"
msgid "Ah! Ah!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W003
msgctxt "602W003"
msgid "Aha! There's the door! I'll be out of here in no time!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W004
msgctxt "602W004"
msgid "Well, so much for those nasty robo-rodents. No wait, this one's still kickin'!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W005
msgctxt "602W005"
msgid "Oh no... I spoke too soon!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W006
msgctxt "602W006"
msgid "Such fussy eaters. They've hardly touched their food at all."
msgstr ""

#: 602W007
msgctxt "602W007"
msgid "Well, that's not going anywhere. It's attached to the cage."
msgstr ""

#: 602W009
msgctxt "602W009"
msgid "Gerbil chow. Best gerbil food money can buy. Keeps their coats nice and shiny."
msgstr ""

#: 602W010
msgctxt "602W010"
msgid "I already have some kibble."
msgstr ""

#: 602W011
msgctxt "602W011"
msgid "I don't have any kibble."
msgstr ""

#: 602W012X
msgctxt "602W012X"
msgid "Hardest ball bearings!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W012Y
msgctxt "602W012Y"
msgid "Pfft, pfft..."
msgstr ""

#: 602W012Z
msgctxt "602W012Z"
msgid "Eugh, tastes like ball bearings too. How do they eat this junk?"
msgstr ""

#: 602W013
msgctxt "602W013"
msgid "Winona hid behind that wheel for weeks when Charlie and Louie were feeling frisky last spring. Oh, memories."
msgstr ""

#: 602W014
msgctxt "602W014"
msgid "Yeah, right!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W015
msgctxt "602W015"
msgid "Alright, the door is opening. And those space creeps thought I wouldn't get out of here."
msgstr ""

#: 602W016A
msgctxt "602W016A"
msgid "He... He... He..."
msgstr ""

#: 602W016B
msgctxt "602W016B"
msgid "HEH HEH HEH HEH"
msgstr ""

#: 602W016C
msgctxt "602W016C"
msgid "Ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha."
msgstr ""

#: 602W016D
msgctxt "602W016D"
msgid "Ah, ah, ah, ah..."
msgstr ""

#: 602W017A
msgctxt "602W017A"
msgid "Phew! I should have worn my sweats!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W017B
msgctxt "602W017B"
msgid "Man, I'm way out of shape."
msgstr ""

#: 602W017C
msgctxt "602W017C"
msgid "Oh, this is really tiring!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W017D
msgctxt "602W017D"
msgid "Man, what a workout!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W017E
msgctxt "602W017E"
msgid "Oh, my gym teacher is right. My sweat does have a pleasant odor."
msgstr ""

#: 602W017F
msgctxt "602W017F"
msgid "This is getting nowhere fast."
msgstr ""

#: 602W017G
msgctxt "602W017G"
msgid "Phew!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W018
msgctxt "602W018"
msgid "Uh-oh."
msgstr ""

#: 602W019
msgctxt "602W019"
msgid "HUAH!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W020
msgctxt "602W020"
msgid "Hmm, I guess this is going to be tougher than I thought. There's gotta be a way to keep that door open."
msgstr ""

#: 602W021
msgctxt "602W021"
msgid "Hmm... that's odd. Some kind of generator is connected to the exercise wheel."
msgstr ""

#: 602W022
msgctxt "602W022"
msgid "The generator seems to power the magnet when the exercise wheel is turning."
msgstr ""

#: 602W023
msgctxt "602W023"
msgid "I can't reach it."
msgstr ""

#: 602W024
msgctxt "602W024"
msgid "Hmm... I never noticed a magnet up there before, and it seems to be connected to that generator thingy."
msgstr ""

#: 602W025
msgctxt "602W025"
msgid "The magnet raises the door while the generator is running."
msgstr ""

#: 602W026
msgctxt "602W026"
msgid "I'll just open this door and I am out of here!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W027
msgctxt "602W027"
msgid "Hmm. Wheel turns, door opens. Wheel stops turning, door closes again."
msgstr ""

#: 602W028
msgctxt "602W028"
msgid "That door is too heavy to lift."
msgstr ""

#: 602W029
msgctxt "602W029"
msgid "Wheel turns, door opens. Wheel stops turning, door closes again."
msgstr ""

#: 602W030
msgctxt "602W030"
msgid "Well, BUDGE!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W031
msgctxt "602W031"
msgid "Well, maybe I'm not so smart after all."
msgstr ""

#: 602W032
msgctxt "602W032"
msgid "Let's do it! Heavy!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W033
msgctxt "602W033"
msgid "I'm sorry it had to come to this, guys, but I do have a planet to save."
msgstr ""

#: 602W034
msgctxt "602W034"
msgid "Well, at least I won't starve in here. I mean, just one of these peanuts could last me a month!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W035
msgctxt "602W035"
msgid "That's too big to lug around."
msgstr ""

#: 602W036
msgctxt "602W036"
msgid "I'll leave it there in case I get hungry later."
msgstr ""

#: 602W037
msgctxt "602W037"
msgid "That tube goes up to the other levels of the cage."
msgstr ""

#: 602W038
msgctxt "602W038"
msgid "That tube goes up to the middle level of the cage."
msgstr ""

#: 602W039
msgctxt "602W039"
msgid "I can't get up there."
msgstr ""

#: 602W040
msgctxt "602W040"
msgid "I'm not getting out that way."
msgstr ""

#: 602W041
msgctxt "602W041"
msgid "Ugh! Dirty!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W042
msgctxt "602W042"
msgid "It's covered with smothering mutant gerbil carcasses."
msgstr ""

#: 602W043
msgctxt "602W043"
msgid "Huh, it didn't leave a mark or nothing."
msgstr ""

#: 602W044
msgctxt "602W044"
msgid "Well, that didn't help a whole lot."
msgstr ""

#: 602W045
msgctxt "602W045"
msgid "NOTHING!"
msgstr ""

#: 602W046
msgctxt "602W046"
msgid "I'm not blasting my way out of here, that's for sure."
msgstr ""

#: 602W047
msgctxt "602W047"
msgid "Nah, it's already dry roasted."
msgstr ""

#: 602W048
msgctxt "602W048"
msgid "Nah, I think I'll hang on to it."
msgstr ""

#: 603W001
msgctxt "603W001"
msgid "WHAAAAAT?"
msgstr ""

#: 603W002
msgctxt "603W002"
msgid "A plastic water dish. It's pretty flimsy looking."
msgstr ""

#: 603W003
msgctxt "603W003"
msgid "It's empty."
msgstr ""

#: 603W004
msgctxt "603W004"
msgid "That's not going anywhere. It's attached to the cage."
msgstr ""

#: 603W006
msgctxt "603W006"
msgid "Cool, refreshing H2O."
msgstr ""

#: 603W007
msgctxt "603W007"
msgid "Oh"
msgstr ""

#: 603W008
msgctxt "603W008"
msgid "Whoa! This thing must weigh a ton!"
msgstr ""

#: 603W009
msgctxt "603W009"
msgid "Not gonna happen. It's bigger than I am. Way bigger!"
msgstr ""

#: 603W010
msgctxt "603W010"
msgid "I'm sure Aunt Polly would know what to do with this thing, but I sure don't."
msgstr ""

#: 603W011
msgctxt "603W011"
msgid "That tube goes up to the top level of the cage."
msgstr ""

#: 603W012
msgctxt "603W012"
msgid "That tube goes down to the bottom level of the cage."
msgstr ""

#: 603W013
msgctxt "603W013"
msgid "I'm not getting out that way."
msgstr ""

#: 603W014
msgctxt "603W014"
msgid "What a mess! There's kibble all over the floor. At least I hope it's kibble."
msgstr ""

#: 603W015
msgctxt "603W015"
msgid "Wow! Something down there was hot!"
msgstr ""

#: 603W016
msgctxt "603W016"
msgid "That ought to cool off that motor."
msgstr ""

#: 603W017
msgctxt "603W017"
msgid "I already zapped a hole in it."
msgstr ""

#: 603W018
msgctxt "603W018"
msgid "That didn't do a whole lot."
msgstr ""

#: 603W019
msgctxt "603W019"
msgid "I can't stand the smell of burning carrots."
msgstr ""

#: 603W020
msgctxt "603W020"
msgid "Well, what do you know? Kibble doesn't float!"
msgstr ""

#: 603W021
msgctxt "603W021"
msgid "Hmm."
msgstr ""

#: 604I001
msgctxt "604I001"
msgid "Ugh..."
msgstr ""

#: 604I003
msgctxt "604I003"
msgid "Yes!"
msgstr ""

#: 604I004
msgctxt "604I004"
msgid "Well, sounds easy enough."
msgstr ""

#: 604I005
msgctxt "604I005"
msgid "Weapon? Wait a minute, what do I need a weapon for?"
msgstr ""

#: 604W001
msgctxt "604W001"
msgid "Getting out of here will be a piece of cake. There's a door on the bottom level."
msgstr ""

#: 604W002
msgctxt "604W002"
msgid "Well, if at first you don't succeed..."
msgstr ""

#: 604W003
msgctxt "604W003"
msgid "Déjà vu!"
msgstr ""

#: 604W004
msgctxt "604W004"
msgid "I'll get out of here this time."
msgstr ""

#: 604W005
msgctxt "604W005"
msgid "Here I go again."
msgstr ""

#: 604W006
msgctxt "604W006"
msgid "Uh-oh."
msgstr ""

#: 604W007
msgctxt "604W007"
msgid "Sounds like my gerbils are snoozing in there."
msgstr ""

#: 604W008
msgctxt "604W008"
msgid "Let's see. I'm two inches tall, I'm locked in a teensy-weensy gerbil cage on a spaceship no less. These psychotic laser totem robo rodents want to use me for target practice, and Earth life as we know it stands a very good chance of being ground into burger meat for an alien fast food chain. Man, I should have just stayed in bed this morning."
msgstr ""

#: 604W009
msgctxt "604W009"
msgid "No more mutant gerbils, just a stinky old pile of wood shavings."
msgstr ""

#: 604W010
msgctxt "604W010"
msgid "Nah."
msgstr ""

#: 604W011
msgctxt "604W011"
msgid "Charlie, Louie, Winona, wake up! It's me, Wilbur!"
msgstr ""

#: 604W012
msgctxt "604W012"
msgid "You're not my gerbils. You're not gerbils at all. My mistake. Just go back to sleep."
msgstr ""

#: 604W013
msgctxt "604W013"
msgid "Hey, you flying furballs!"
msgstr ""

#: 604W014
msgctxt "604W014"
msgid "If you want me, come and get me!"
msgstr ""

#: 604W015
msgctxt "604W015"
msgid "Disintegrated wood chips!"
msgstr ""

#: 604W016
msgctxt "604W016"
msgid "Nah, I just get dirty."
msgstr ""

#: 604W017
msgctxt "604W017"
msgid "Phew! I should have cleaned out this cage when I had the chance. This apple stinks!"
msgstr ""

#: 604W018
msgctxt "604W018"
msgid "Right. It's bigger than I am."
msgstr ""

#: 604W019
msgctxt "604W019"
msgid "I'm not touching that smelly thing. It's rotten to the core. Literally."
msgstr ""

#: 604W020
msgctxt "604W020"
msgid "Enormous!"
msgstr ""

#: 604W021
msgctxt "604W021"
msgid "Oh, that's too big to lug around."
msgstr ""

#: 604W022
msgctxt "604W022"
msgid "That tube goes down to the middle level of the cage."
msgstr ""

#: 604W024
msgctxt "604W024"
msgid "That tube goes down to the other levels of the cage."
msgstr ""

#: 604W025
msgctxt "604W025"
msgid "I'm not getting out that way."
msgstr ""

#: 604W026
msgctxt "604W026"
msgid "Ugh! Dirty!"
msgstr ""

#: 604W027
msgctxt "604W027"
msgid "I don't want to hurt my gerbils."
msgstr ""

#: 604W028
msgctxt "604W028"
msgid "Eat photons, you mutated robo-rodents!"
msgstr ""

#: 604W029
msgctxt "604W029"
msgid "Nah, that would probably make it smell even worse."
msgstr ""

#: 604Z002
msgctxt "604Z002"
msgid "HAHAHAHAHAHA"
msgstr ""

#: 604Z003
msgctxt "604Z003"
msgid "Did I scare you?"
msgstr ""

#: 604Z004A
msgctxt "604Z004A"
msgid "Good! Now listen up. Intelligence is defined as the capacity to adapt, survive and flourish."
msgstr ""

#: 604Z004B
msgctxt "604Z004B"
msgid "This is where we test the SURVIVE part of the definition."
msgstr ""

#: 604Z004C
msgctxt "604Z004C"
msgid "To pass, all you have to do is find your way out of the cage. Dad, dad."
msgstr ""

#: 604Z005
msgctxt "604Z005"
msgid "You will see about that."
msgstr ""

#: 604Z006
msgctxt "604Z006"
msgid "Flemix, issue him a weapon!"
msgstr ""

#: 604Z007
msgctxt "604Z007"
msgid "So many questions for such a little man. Yeah, yeah, yeah."
msgstr ""

#: 605W001
msgctxt "605W001"
msgid "You guys can talk? Oh no! No, no, no! WAAAH!"
msgstr ""

#: 605W002E
msgctxt "605W002E"
msgid "Oh no! No, no, no! Don't shoot!"
msgstr ""

#: 605X001
msgctxt "605X001"
msgid "Locked on Lifesign... FIREWING!"
msgstr ""

#: 606W003B
msgctxt "606W003B"
msgid "Nooooooo!"
msgstr ""

#: 606W003D
msgctxt "606W003D"
msgid "Ah! Let me outta here!"
msgstr ""

#: 606X001
msgctxt "606X001"
msgid "I thought I'd find... FIRE FIRE FIRE FIRE!"
msgstr ""

#: 608F001
msgctxt "608F001"
msgid "If that was the suicide test, you would have passed with flying colors."
msgstr ""

#: 608F002A
msgctxt "608F002A"
msgid "Back to earth with you, buddy!"
msgstr ""

#: 608F003A
msgctxt "608F003A"
msgid "I don't know what you did in there, but you sure made a mess of things."
msgstr ""

#: 608F004A
msgctxt "608F004A"
msgid "Survival instincts. Ha! Sometimes I think these creatures actually want to be burger meat."
msgstr ""

#: 609W001
msgctxt "609W001"
msgid "Holy smokes! They're blasting each other to kingdom come!"
