msgctxt "804Z001"
msgid "A hundred billion Neurosites!"
msgstr ""

#: 804Z002
msgctxt "804Z002"
msgid "It's pitiful!"
msgstr ""

#: 804Z003
msgctxt "804Z003"
msgid "I'm amazed that this creature was able to crawl out of the primordial ooze with such a sorry excuse for a brain."
msgstr ""

#: 805W001
msgctxt "805W001"
msgid "OUGLELELELELELE-"
msgstr ""

#: 806F002
msgctxt "806F002"
msgid "INCREDIBLE!"
msgstr ""

#: 806F003
msgctxt "806F003"
msgid "His neurosynaptic bandwidth is right off the scale for a Gamma class life form."
msgstr ""

#: 806W001
msgctxt "806W001"
msgid "No!"
msgstr ""

#: 806W001A
msgctxt "806W001A"
msgid "Ha! No!"
msgstr ""

#: 806W001C
msgctxt "806W001C"
msgid "OOOH!"
msgstr ""

#: 806W001D
msgctxt "806W001D"
msgid "NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO"
msgstr ""

#: 806W001E
msgctxt "806W001E"
msgid "Waaaaaaaaaaaaaaah!"
msgstr ""

#: 806W001F
msgctxt "806W001F"
msgid "OOOOOHOOHOOHOHOHOH!"
msgstr ""

#: 806W001G
msgctxt "806W001G"
msgid "Waaah!"
msgstr ""

#: 806Z001
msgctxt "806Z001"
msgid "What a huge surprise! His minuscule brain barely conducts at all!"
msgstr ""

#: 806Z002
msgctxt "806Z002"
msgid "Gah-hah-hah!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0101
msgctxt "80N0101"
msgid "Why, neurosynaptic testing, of course!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0201
msgctxt "80N0201"
msgid "Oh, how rude of me. I am Flummox, and this is Senior Protein Procurement Agent Slarg."
msgstr ""

#: 80N0202
msgctxt "80N0202"
msgid "That's right! We're purveyors of premium protein for Orion Burger, Incorporated, the largest fast-food chain in the entire galaxy! Your planet has been identified as a candidate for protein harvesting!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0203
msgctxt "80N0203"
msgid "You are in geosynchronous orbit directly above your Earth settlement."
msgstr ""

#: 80N0204
msgctxt "80N0204"
msgid "We're testing you to find out if Earthlings are intelligent or not. You see, intelligent life is an extremely scarce resource in the universe. We wouldn't want to grind it up in our Orion burgers by accident, would we, boss?"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0205
msgctxt "80N0205"
msgid "No, we don't test leaders anymore. They were failing our intelligence tests so badly that we had to switch to randomly selected test specimens. So, you're our randomly selected Earthling!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0206
msgctxt "80N0206"
msgid "That's neurosynaptic testing, bucko! Quite simply, we're going to apply a simulated nerve impulse to your cerebral cortex and measure how much juice your primitive little noodle can handle."
msgstr ""

#: 80N0207
msgctxt "80N0207"
msgid "They're electrodes, you ninny! Can't apply simulated nerve impulses without electrodes!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0208
msgctxt "80N0208"
msgid "Just relax your nerve fibers and conduct as much of the impulse as you possibly can."
msgstr ""

#: 80N0209
msgctxt "80N0209"
msgid "Hello! Are you paying any attention at all? If you fail, we harvest your planet!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0301
msgctxt "80N0301"
msgid "That's the general idea, human!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0401
msgctxt "80N0401"
msgid "Oh joy, Flummox! We found ourselves a complete idiot!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0402
msgctxt "80N0402"
msgid "Yeah! Imagine being in geosynchronous orbit without a spaceship! Ha ha ha ha ha! Oh, that's rich!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0501
msgctxt "80N0501"
msgid "Oh, of course not! That would be just too... terrible!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0701
msgctxt "80N0701"
msgid "Gee, uh, I don't know. Does it hurt, boss?"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0702
msgctxt "80N0702"
msgid "With any luck at all, it'll be excruciating!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0901
msgctxt "80N0901"
msgid "Speaking of harvesting, Flammocks, get on with the test!"
msgstr ""

#: 80N0902
msgctxt "80N0902"
msgid "Okay, boss!"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0101
msgctxt "80P0101"
msgid "Um, am I ready for what?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0201
msgctxt "80P0201"
msgid "Who are you guys?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0202
msgctxt "80P0202"
msgid "Protein Procurement Agent?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0203
msgctxt "80P0203"
msgid "Where am I?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0204
msgctxt "80P0204"
msgid "Why are you testing me?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0205
msgctxt "80P0205"
msgid "Don't you want me to take you to my leader?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0206
msgctxt "80P0206"
msgid "Um, what is neuro... whatchamacallit, testing?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0207
msgctxt "80P0207"
msgid "What are these things on my head?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0208
msgctxt "80P0208"
msgid "What do I have to do to pass this test?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0209
msgctxt "80P0209"
msgid "What happens if I fail the test?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0301
msgctxt "80P0301"
msgid "So, uh, you guys are gonna make hamburgers out of me?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0401
msgctxt "80P0401"
msgid "You mean this is a spaceship?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0601
msgctxt "80P0601"
msgid "Haha, lucky me!"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0701
msgctxt "80P0701"
msgid "Simulated nerve impulse? Um... Will it hurt?"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0801
msgctxt "80P0801"
msgid "That's what I was afraid of!"
msgstr ""

#: 80P0903
msgctxt "80P0903"
msgid "Be gentle!"
msgstr ""

#: 81N0101
msgctxt "81N0101"
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr ""

#: 81N0201
msgctxt "81N0201"
msgid "Headache? Yeah, sure. I got something for your headache."
msgstr ""

#: 81N0202
msgctxt "81N0202"
msgid "It's an Abduct-A-Tron Model 2000, I think. I'm going to use it to send you back to Earth, to the exact time and place that you were abducted from."
msgstr ""

#: 81N0203
msgctxt "81N0203"
msgid "Don't be silly, you failed the test. Of course you are going to beat Burger Meat, you and the rest of your sorry planet."
msgstr ""

#: 81N0204
msgctxt "81N0204"
msgid "What's to talk about? I'm starving!"
msgstr ""

#: 81N0205
msgctxt "81N0205"
msgid "Oh, that? That's just a neutrino pulse gun. I fire it at your brain, and it erases your chartreuse memory. Nothing to get worked up about."
msgstr ""

#: 81N0206
msgctxt "81N0206"
msgid "Boy, you're just full of questions, aren't you? Well, for your information, I have to erase your memory. It's standard abduction protocol. You see, we send you back to the exact time and place we snatched you from, with no memory of your abduction. That way, you don't know you were gone, and no one else knows you were gone either. Pretty clever, don't you think?"
msgstr ""

#: 81N0301
msgctxt "81N0301"
msgid "Don't you think I have better things to do than lug you all the way back down to the cargo hold? I'm sending you back to Earth, so that we can harvest you with the rest of your pathetic species."
msgstr ""

#: 81N0401
msgctxt "81N0401"
msgid "Of course, none of this matters a whole lot in your case. You know, with your planet about to be harvested and all."
msgstr ""

#: 81N0402
msgctxt "81N0402"
msgid "Alright, we're ready to go."
msgstr ""

#: 81N0403
msgctxt "81N0403"
msgid "On behalf of all the nice folks in Orion Burger's Protein Procurement Division, I would like to thank you for your cooperation during our testing procedures. Have a super day!"
msgstr ""

#: 81P0101
msgctxt "81P0101"
msgid "Ah, excuse me."
msgstr ""

#: 81P0201
msgctxt "81P0201"
msgid "Do you have anything for a headache?"
msgstr ""

#: 81P0202
msgctxt "81P0202"
msgid "What is this thing that I'm in?"
msgstr ""

#: 81P0203
msgctxt "81P0203"
msgid "Phew! I thought I was going to be burger meat!"
msgstr ""

#: 81P0204
msgctxt "81P0204"
msgid "Uh, c-couldn't we talk this over?"
msgstr ""

#: 81P0205
msgctxt "81P0205"
msgid "Why is that gun thingy pointing at my head?"
msgstr ""

#: 81P0206
msgctxt "81P0206"
msgid "Why are you erasing my memory?"
msgstr ""

#: 81P0301
msgctxt "81P0301"
msgid "So, why are you sending me back to Earth, then?"
msgstr ""

#: 81P0401
msgctxt "81P0401"
msgid "I suppose so."
msgstr ""

#: 81P0402
msgctxt "81P0402"
msgid "I suppose not."
msgstr ""

#: 82N0101
msgctxt "82N0101"
msgid "That's funny. I don't feel so great either. I must be coming down with something."
msgstr ""

#: 82N0201
msgctxt "82N0201"
msgid "I think so. No, wait. I seem to have misplaced my legs... and my nose."
msgstr ""

#: 82N0202
msgctxt "82N0202"
msgid "No... uh... what happened?"
msgstr ""

#: 82N0203
msgctxt "82N0203"
msgid "Uh, I'm... I'm really confused right now."
msgstr ""

#: 82N0204
msgctxt "82N0204"
msgid "Oh, yeah. You're Swarg, my wonderful boss."
msgstr ""

#: 82N0205
msgctxt "82N0205"
msgid "You forgot where the meat blocker is? You must be a little confused too. Follow me, boss."
msgstr ""

#: 82N0206
msgctxt "82N0206"
msgid "Human? I don't know. I guess he got away from me somehow."
msgstr ""

#: 82N0207
msgctxt "82N0207"
msgid "Oh, lost your keys? I'm having one of those days too, boss."
msgstr ""

#: 82N0301
msgctxt "82N0301"
msgid "Oh, don't worry about that. I'll clean it up later, boss."
msgstr ""

#: 82P0101
msgctxt "82P0101"
msgid "You're looking pretty out of it, Flummox."
msgstr ""

#: 82P0201
msgctxt "82P0201"
msgid "Can you stand on one leg and touch your nose?"
msgstr ""

#: 82P0202
msgctxt "82P0202"
msgid "You look lost. Do you know where you are?"
msgstr ""

#: 82P0203
msgctxt "82P0203"
msgid "Do you know who you are?"
msgstr ""

#: 82P0204
msgctxt "82P0204"
msgid "Do you know who I am?"
msgstr ""

#: 82P0205
msgctxt "82P0205"
msgid "I'm hungry. Where is my meat locker?"
msgstr ""

#: 82P0206
msgctxt "82P0206"
msgid "Where is the human? Y-you moron!"
msgstr ""

#: 82P0207
msgctxt "82P0207"
msgid "How do you get these big doors to open?"
msgstr ""

#: 82P0301
msgctxt "82P0301"
msgid "I'm not sure, but you sure made a mess of the Abduct-A-Tron."
msgstr ""

#: 82P0401
msgctxt "82P0401"
msgid "BOSS!"
msgstr ""

#: 83N0101
msgctxt "83N0101"
msgid "I didn't think I'd see you again. How did you escape?"
msgstr ""

#: 83N0201
msgctxt "83N0201"
msgid "I will be, after I thaw out a bit more."
msgstr ""

#: 83N0202
msgctxt "83N0202"
msgid "He went to the bridge to harvest your planet. Uh... why are we whispering?"
msgstr ""

#: 83N0203
msgctxt "83N0203"
msgid "I wish I could, but I can hardly move right now, except to shiver. You better go on without me."
msgstr ""

#: 83N0204
msgctxt "83N0204"
msgid "Every one of these creatures is from a planet that's already been harvested. And I'll bet that they're all intelligent life forms."
msgstr ""

#: 83N0205
msgctxt "83N0205"
msgid "How are you going to stop him?"
msgstr ""

#: 83N0301
msgctxt "83N0301"
msgid "You're kidding! That's amazing!"
msgstr ""

#: 83N0401
msgctxt "83N0401"
msgid "Yeah, no fooling. And I would have been Zlog's lunch if you hadn't saved me."
msgstr ""

#: 83N0501
msgctxt "83N0501"
msgid "I... I see. Well, good luck!"
msgstr ""

#: 83P0102
msgctxt "83P0102"
msgid "Well, things were a little dicey at first, but then I took a moment to reflect on my situation, and well, a solution just sort of hit me."
msgstr ""

#: 83P0201
msgctxt "83P0201"
msgid "Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

#: 83P0202
msgctxt "83P0202"
msgid "Which way did Zlar go?"
msgstr ""

#: 83P0203
msgctxt "83P0203"
msgid "Will you help me stop the harvest?"
msgstr ""

#: 83P0204
msgctxt "83P0204"
msgid "Ugh! What a creepy place this is!"
msgstr ""

#: 83P0205
msgctxt "83P0205"
msgid "Take care, Astral! I'm gonna stop Zlarg now!"
msgstr ""

#: 83P0301
msgctxt "83P0301"
msgid "I don't want Bubblebutt to hear us. He thinks that I'm Zlarg."
msgstr ""

#: 83P0401
msgctxt "83P0401"
msgid "Unbelievable! I guess that gluttonous green glob likes to keep a few choice cuts aside for himself!"
msgstr ""

#: 83P0501
msgctxt "83P0501"
msgid "I haven't thought that far ahead, but I'm sure that something will come to me."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0201
msgctxt "84N0201"
msgid "Oh yeah, yeah, you'd have to go clear over the... clear over the Boonsville to find quality like this. Straight!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0202
msgctxt "84N0202"
msgid "Is that so? Well, then you sir, you make some of the finest swill in the state."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0203
msgctxt "84N0203"
msgid "Well, no wonder it's so good! I gotta get me a case of this school, isn't it, bro?"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0204
msgctxt "84N0204"
msgid "Yeah, yeah, tell us, what's your secret ingredient, Elminer?"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0205
msgctxt "84N0205"
msgid "I could be happier. Actually, I'm kind of concerned about my new best buddy, Elmer. He's a little down in the dumps right now. I won't be happy until I figure out a way to lift his spirits, you know what I mean?"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0206
msgctxt "84N0206"
msgid "Ah, you and your space aliens. And the kid says he doesn't drink. Yeah, I believe that."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0207
msgctxt "84N0207"
msgid "You can go away, and leave us alone!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0208
msgctxt "84N0208"
msgid "Of course not, Island Stealer. We ain't got no still."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0209
msgctxt "84N0209"
msgid "I'll see you later, Wilbur!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0210
msgctxt "84N0210"
msgid "Good riddance, the island stealer!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0301
msgctxt "84N0301"
msgid "This is Bonesville, ya twit!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0302
msgctxt "84N0302"
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0303
msgctxt "84N0303"
msgid "Boy, I must be even more looped than I thought. And I knew I was sort of looped."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0401
msgctxt "84N0401"
msgid "Glad you like it, doody!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0402
msgctxt "84N0402"
msgid "The name is Stolie-um-um-er."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0501
msgctxt "84N0501"
msgid "You can't. That's the last bottle, and I ain't got my still no more. This little hoolum swiped it for me."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0502
msgctxt "84N0502"
msgid "Say it ain't so, Wilbur!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0601
msgctxt "84N0601"
msgid "Rotten Cabbage!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0602
msgctxt "84N0602"
msgid "Oh, well, that explains the exquisite bouquet."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0701
msgctxt "84N0701"
msgid "Exactly why do you want to make us happy? What do you say? Kind of a good samaritan?"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0702
msgctxt "84N0702"
msgid "If you ask me, you're a jerk!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0703
msgctxt "84N0703"
msgid "Why are you so mean to the boy?"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0704
msgctxt "84N0704"
msgid "Cuz he screwed some cockamamie deed in my face and scraped everything I own. Now I got no island, no mine, no house, no steel, no nothing."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0705
msgctxt "84N0705"
msgid "Say it ain't so, Wilbur!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0801
msgctxt "84N0801"
msgid "Oh, he did, did he?"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0802
msgctxt "84N0802"
msgid "Well, that's no excuse, Wilbur. If you really wanted to save the world, you'd let us make some more of that... that heavenly nectar."
msgstr ""

#: 84N0901
msgctxt "84N0901"
msgid "Hey! Where did the town hall go?"
msgstr ""

#: 84N0902
msgctxt "84N0902"
msgid "I blasted it to smithereens! That's where it went!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N1001
msgctxt "84N1001"
msgid "You know, I bet if we bottle that stuff and put like a nice yuppie label on it, we can make zillions! Hey, what do you say? You can be the broom-meister, huh? And I'll be the brains!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N1002
msgctxt "84N1002"
msgid "Great idea, brains! Except for one small thing. We ain't got no still!"
msgstr ""

#: 84N1003
msgctxt "84N1003"
msgid "Oh, yeah. Well, I didn't say I had all the details of the work, so give me a break, okay?"
msgstr ""

#: 84P0201
msgctxt "84P0201"
msgid "Is Elmo's rotgut really that good?"
msgstr ""

#: 84P0202
msgctxt "84P0202"
msgid "Elmo made that hooch himself!"
msgstr ""

#: 84P0203
msgctxt "84P0203"
msgid "Elmo aged that hooch for an entire two weeks!"
msgstr ""

#: 84P0204
msgctxt "84P0204"
msgid "What is that hooch made from?"
msgstr ""

#: 84P0205
msgctxt "84P0205"
msgid "Are you happy, Stolie?"
msgstr ""

#: 84P0206
msgctxt "84P0206"
msgid "Space Aliens said I have to make you guys happy!"
msgstr ""

#: 84P0207
msgctxt "84P0207"
msgid "What can I do to make you guys happy?"
msgstr ""

#: 84P0208
msgctxt "84P0208"
msgid "Making any progress in the moonshine business?"
msgstr ""

#: 84P0209
msgctxt "84P0209"
msgid "I gotta go now."
msgstr ""

#: 84P0210
msgctxt "84P0210"
msgid "I gotta go now."
msgstr ""

#: 84P0702
msgctxt "84P0702"
msgid "I'm just a nice guy."
msgstr ""

#: 84P0801
msgctxt "84P0801"
msgid "It's all nice and legal. Gus sold it to me."
msgstr ""

#: 84P0802
msgctxt "84P0802"
msgid "I had to take it! I'm trying to save the Earth!"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0201
msgctxt "86N0201"
msgid "Huh? Oh, Roxy's mad at me. Again!"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0401
msgctxt "86N0401"
msgid "Not particularly."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0402
msgctxt "86N0402"
msgid "Well, on top of getting us lost, causing us to miss our gig and misplacing some of the band's equipment, it turns out that today is our leather anniversary, which of course I totally forgot. Oh, it's just not my day, I tell you. Just not my day at all."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0403
msgctxt "86N0403"
msgid "Yeah, that's right. The big one, you know. Oh, man. I can't believe I forgot!"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0404
msgctxt "86N0404"
msgid "Nope, not all one."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0405
msgctxt "86N0405"
msgid "These are all my worldly possessions. Roxy threw them at me, told me to get lost. Pretty sad, isn't it? All I've got is a guitar, a box of old records, and the clothes on my back."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0406
msgctxt "86N0406"
msgid "I'm sorry to disappoint you and your little green friends, man, but I'm not feeling very chipper at the moment."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0407
msgctxt "86N0407"
msgid "Yeah, whatever."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0501
msgctxt "86N0501"
msgid "Oh, half the time I don't even know what city I'm in, let alone what day it is. You know, life on the road and all. It's a bloody occupational hazard, I tell you."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0502
msgctxt "86N0502"
msgid "Oh, are you a musician too?"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0503
msgctxt "86N0503"
msgid "Yeah, yeah, we've been through a lot together. Oh, seems like only yesterday we was touring with the yard turtles."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0504
msgctxt "86N0504"
msgid "Nah, it will take more than a few days to patch things over this time, man. I've never seen her this mad before. I'm afraid this is the end of the road for us. And the group too."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0505
msgctxt "86N0505"
msgid "Well, I didn't realize you were such a big fan."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0506
msgctxt "86N0506"
msgid "Oh, I really don't know. But I suppose if I had a proper anniversary gift for her, I wouldn't be in this mess in the first place."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0507
msgctxt "86N0507"
msgid "What, you daft? I can't just give her any old thing. You know, it is our leather anniversary after all. Why, it would have to be something, you know, appropriate for the occasion. You know, something that shows our care. You know, something, I don't know, something, well, you know, something hip."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0508
msgctxt "86N0508"
msgid "Oh, you're a riot, you are. There isn't a hip anniversary gift to be found within miles of this dreary little burg."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0509
msgctxt "86N0509"
msgid "Last year was our tattoo anniversary. Yeah, it was an easy one, right? Biggest problem I had was finding enough real estate on her for another tattoo."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0510
msgctxt "86N0510"
msgid "Yeah, well, whatever."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0601
msgctxt "86N0601"
msgid "Oh man, I'm having a rotten day as it is. Don't be laying some kind of space alien trip on me, alright?"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0701
msgctxt "86N0701"
msgid "I didn't think he was a musician."
msgstr ""

#: 86N0801
msgctxt "86N0801"
msgid "Why on earth would I give you my guitar?"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0802
msgctxt "86N0802"
msgid "Are you kidding me? I just told you this was all I had left in the world. What's the matter with you?"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0803
msgctxt "86N0803"
msgid "Why on earth would I give you my record collection?"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0804
msgctxt "86N0804"
msgid "Are you kidding me? I just told you this was all I have left in the world. What's the matter with you?"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0805
msgctxt "86N0805"
msgid "Oh, then I would be eternally grateful. Now, buzz off!"
msgstr ""

#: 86N0806
msgctxt "86N0806"
msgid "Yeah, right."
msgstr ""

#: 86P0201
msgctxt "86P0201"
msgid "Why so glum, buddy?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0401
msgctxt "86P0401"
msgid "Wanna talk about it?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0402
msgctxt "86P0402"
msgid "Why is Roxy mad at you?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0403
msgctxt "86P0403"
msgid "Leather anniversary?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0404
msgctxt "86P0404"
msgid "Any leather anniversary gift ideas yet?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0405
msgctxt "86P0405"
msgid "What is all your stuff doing here?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0406
msgctxt "86P0406"
msgid "Space aliens say I have to make you happy."
msgstr ""

#: 86P0407
msgctxt "86P0407"
msgid "I'll let you go back to your moping now."
msgstr ""

#: 86P0501
msgctxt "86P0501"
msgid "How did you forget such an important anniversary?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0502
msgctxt "86P0502"
msgid "I don't know what day it is either."
msgstr ""

#: 86P0503
msgctxt "86P0503"
msgid "Have you and Roxy been together for a long time?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0504
msgctxt "86P0504"
msgid "Maybe you should send her some flowers."
msgstr ""

#: 86P0505
msgctxt "86P0505"
msgid "You can't give up on her. The world needs you."
msgstr ""

#: 86P0506
msgctxt "86P0506"
msgid "How can you smooth things over with her?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0507
msgctxt "86P0507"
msgid "Why don't you get her an anniversary gift then?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0508
msgctxt "86P0508"
msgid "So, get her something hip!"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0509
msgctxt "86P0509"
msgid "What did you get her for your last anniversary?"
msgstr ""

#: 86P0510
msgctxt "86P0510"
msgid "I'll let you get back to your moping now."
msgstr ""

